Ha ha!
[snorts]

1267
01:10:48,900 --> 01:10:51,000
He's back
To his old self.

1268
01:10:51,200 --> 01:10:53,600
Thank god.

1269
01:10:54,300 --> 01:10:56,600
[laughing]

1270
