Good morning.

1285
01:11:45,000 --> 01:11:47,100
...evening,
And good night.

1286
01:11:47,300 --> 01:11:50,000
Morning.
Morning, spencer.

1287
01:11:50,000 --> 01:11:51,000
How's it going?

1288
01:11:51,200 --> 01:11:52,500
Hmm, let me check.

1289
