01:11:58,600 --> 01:11:59,600
Both:
Good morning, truman!

1293
01:11:59,900 --> 01:12:01,900
Oh, look who's here.

1294
01:12:02,100 --> 01:12:03,100
Beautiful day,
Isn't it?

1295
01:12:03,300 --> 01:12:04,000
Every single day.

1296
01:12:04,200 --> 01:12:05,800
The policy--
We've thought about it...

1297
01:12:06,000 --> 01:12:07,100
